## 30-second quickstart

```sh
composer global require {{.Vendor}}/{{.Name}}
{{.Name}} --help
{{.Name}} --version
```

Every command supports the kit output flag suite:

```sh
{{.Name}} list --format json
{{.Name}} list --format yaml
{{.Name}} list --cols name,status
{{.Name}} list -o results.json   # ext infers format
{{.Name}} list --format-help     # show all formats + options
```

## What {{.Name}} is

Three surfaces, one package:

- **CLI** — interactive + scriptable. Stable schemas, structured errors,
  preview via `--dry-run`, queries parse via `--explain`.
- **Capability surface** — `{{.Name}} spec --format json` emits a
  machine-readable manifest of every command, its inputs, outputs, side
  effects, and idempotency. Agents drive {{.Name}} from this, not from
  `--help`.
- **Library** — `composer require {{.Vendor}}/{{.Name}}` and use the
  same primitives from your own PHP code.

Conformance proof: [`docs/12-factor-conformance.md`](docs/12-factor-conformance.md)
(auto-regenerated by `make conformance`).

